                            <comment id="17945427" author="tdiesler" created="Thu, 17 Apr 2025 14:55:51 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;There is an inconsistency in platform-http headers ...&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;platform-http (vertex)&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
CamelHttpMethod: GET
CamelHttpPath: /&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;protected&lt;/span&gt;
CamelHttpQuery: &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;null&lt;/span&gt;
CamelHttpRawQuery: &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;null&lt;/span&gt;
CamelHttpUri: /&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;protected&lt;/span&gt;
CamelHttpUrl: http:&lt;span class=&quot;code-comment&quot;&gt;//example.local/&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;protected&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;CamelVertxPlatformHttpLocalAddress: 10.1.5.203:8080
CamelVertxPlatformHttpRemoteAddress: 10.1.5.148:58360
Host: example.local
Referer: https:&lt;span class=&quot;code-comment&quot;&gt;//example.local/
&lt;/span&gt;X-Forwarded-For: 192.168.65.3
X-Forwarded-Host: example.local
X-Forwarded-Port: 443
X-Forwarded-Proto: https
X-Forwarded-Server: traefik-85d46678bc-pb9hm
X-Real-Ip: 192.168.65.3
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;platform-http (spring-boot)&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
CamelHttpCharacterEncoding: UTF-8
CamelHttpMethod: GET
CamelHttpPath: 
CamelHttpQuery: &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;null&lt;/span&gt;
CamelHttpServletRequest: org.apache.catalina.connector.RequestFacade@cd7ef85
CamelHttpServletResponse: org.springframework.web.context.request.async.StandardServletAsyncWebRequest$LifecycleHttpServletResponse@8e86ac7
CamelHttpUri: /&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;protected&lt;/span&gt;
CamelHttpUrl: https:&lt;span class=&quot;code-comment&quot;&gt;//example.local/&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;protected&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;CamelPlatformHttpContextPath: /&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;protected&lt;/span&gt;
host: example.local
x-forwarded-host: example.local
x-forwarded-port: 443
x-forwarded-proto: https
x-forwarded-server: traefik-85d46678bc-pb9hm
x-real-ip: 192.168.65.3
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Note, the the difference in CamelHttpPath value.&lt;br/&gt;
Also, spring boot seems to use lower case headers.&lt;br/&gt;
The Message.getHeader APIs do not seem to be case sensitive (undocumented) - the oauth code works with both.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Now using CamelHttpUri instead of CamelHttpPath&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
